<C>__{todd }
<D>__{johanna...}
<C>__{anthony}
<D>__{johanna...}
<L>__{interior barber shop day}
<A>__{...todd shaves a customer. we recognize the customer instantly: it is the gentleman. the daguerreotype now rest on the counter. todd remains wistful, detached, dream like.}
<C>__{todd}
<D>__{and if you're beautiful, what then, with yellow hair, like wheat? i think we shall not meet again }
<P>__{(he quietly slits the gentleman's throat)}
<D>__{my little dove, my sweet...}
<L>__{exterior spitalfields market day}
<A>__{...we see the figure of anthony, walking past hanging carcasses of the busy meat market.}
<C>__{todd }
<D>__{johanna...}
<C>__{anthony}
<D>__{i will steal you, johanna...}
